fields.name: Hestela Charbonnier - Amour et Amour
fields.description:
Colorful airs that are made up of delicate scents that alternate between warm, sometimes sparkling, woody, sweet notes and always present in our tradition
They were created by drawing on distant memories, sensations and moods to make them flow into a torrent of new emotions
and the dance of flowers, the dance of colors, the dance of perfumes, of joys, of smiles that embraces us at every awakening and kisses us at every sunset.

  • TECHNIQUE: Acrylic on canvas
  • SIGNATURE: Hand signed
  • YEAR: 2024
  • EDITION: Unique

fields.name: Ugo Vistosi - Ninfee XL
fields.description:
The painting is a unique and original piece, created with acrylic colors on canvas by Vistosi Ugo, signed at the bottom left by the author, it is shipped rolled up in a sturdy rigid tube.
The canvas measures 160x90, and must be stretched and fixed on a 150x80 cm frame, not supplied, and the edges will also be painted like the painting.
A dreamlike vision between abstraction and figurative characterizes this work, full of pathos and colors.

TECHNIQUE: Acrylic on canvas
SIGNATURE: Hand signed
YEAR: 2024
EDITION: Single piece
CONDITION: Excellent condition
